snippet.title: DAVE THE DIVER | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Exciting news, Divers! 
We're officially swimming out of Steam Early Access with DAVE THE DIVER officially launching June 28. 
Thanks for your unwavering support! Stay geared up—more adventures, features, and enhancements are on the way!


🤿 | Game Introduction | Welcome to 'DAVE THE DIVER', a marine adventure set in the mysterious Blue Hole. Explore the sea with Dave by day, and run a sushi restaurant at night. Uncover the secrets of the Blue Hole, and unwrap this deep sea mystery involving 3 friends, each with distinct personalities. New adventures await.  

🐬Check out more details on DAVE THE DIVER Steam Page and official community channel! 
■ STEAM : [https://nexon.link/5Pc]  
■ Discord: [https://discord.gg/davethediver]  
■ Twitter: [https://twitter.com/DaveDiverGame]  
■ Website: [https://mintrocketgames.com/en/DaveTheDiver]
